17
00:00:43,010 --> 00:00:45,279 line:1
Before we get started,
if this is your first time


18
00:00:45,279 --> 00:00:47,948 position:50%
using SF Symbols,
or if you just want a refresher,


19
00:00:47,948 --> 00:00:49,883 position:50%
I recommend you watch
